<br>
Don't kill the bug critters and they won't give you faction hits and start aggroing on you (The hatchlings don't give faction hits and ARE aggro. ANd blue. And hard to see. But if a bug sees you fighting them, the bug will attack too.)<br>
<br>
The only thing you generally have to worry about are the little rockfiend looking things. They will attack and have LOTS of HPs. <br>
<br>
The rockhoppers won't normally attack you. But they are social if you are fighting anything else. <br>
<br>
There are also some other casters -- ghost-looking things. And these green tentacly things.<br>
<br>
this is NOT a money camp at all though.<br>
<br>
